OL,3,CNo one cared for our safety': Former
OL,4,CHMP Parc employees on working in prison
OL,6,FITV Wales have been told by former
OL,7,Fstaff members at in that they felt
OL,8,Funsafe while working there because of
OL,9,Flow levels of staffing.
OL,11,FStephen Williams was a Officer at Parc
OL,12,Ffor four years before quitting in
OL,13,FMarch. He says he left because of a
OL,14,F"deterioration of prisoners" and
OL,15,F"deterioration of staff".
OL,17,F"When you raised the questions of what
OL,18,Fwe are going to do about it there was
OL,19,Fnothing coming forward. There is staff
OL,20,Fthere doing 24 hour shifts because of
OL,21,Fthe lack of staff to run the facility."
