OL,3,CNo one cared for our safety': Former
OL,4,CHMP Parc employees on working in prison
OL,6,FWe heard from others who also said 24
OL,7,Fhour working and not enough staff for
OL,8,Fthe number of prisoners are a problem.
OL,10,FHe says Parc operates a staffing ratio
OL,11,Fof 33 prisoners to one prison officers-
OL,12,F the minimum level set by the Ministry
OL,13,Fof Justice, but a number far greater
OL,14,Fthan in Government run jails like
OL,15,FCardiff or Swansea.
OL,17,F"I would say it's unsafe and I'd say
OL,18,Fit's not providing what it should be
OL,19,Fproviding." said Stephen.
