OL,6,F"They haven't got enough staff there
OL,7,Fto run the jail safely." It follows
OL,8,Fnine sudden deaths in the Prison since
OL,9,Fthe end of February.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Police has confirmed that
OL,12,Ffour of these deaths involved drugs.
OL,14,FStephen says he's surprised there's
OL,15,Fnot been more deaths.
