OL,6,F"I think there'd be a lot more and I'd
OL,7,Fbe honest with you if it wasn't for
OL,8,Fthe prison officers and healthcare
OL,9,Fstaff front line there probably would
OL,10,Fbe a lot more because the work they do
OL,11,Fis phenomenal based on the resources
OL,12,Fthey have.
OL,14,F"But again prior to the latest nine
OL,15,Fdeaths, I remember submitting a
OL,16,Fwhistleblowing. I think it was in
OL,17,FDecember and I clearly stated within
OL,18,Fthat how many deaths will it take
OL,19,Fwithin Parc before seniors take note?
OL,20,FNothing has changed."
