OL,4,CHMP Parc employees on working in prison
OL,6,FHe says he raised concerns about
OL,7,Fwelfare of staff and prisoners, but
OL,8,Fthey fell on deaf ears.
OL,10,F"I attended a unit, there was a
OL,11,Fhorrific smell coming from a certain
OL,12,Fcell.
OL,14,F"I just approached it, had a look and
OL,15,Fnoticed a person inside, I had a good
OL,16,Frapport with him so had no concerns
OL,17,Fand opened the door and asked what's
OL,18,Fgoing on.
