OL,6,F"He'd been there living in an inch of
OL,7,Fdirty water, soiled water and when I
OL,8,Fasked the prisoners how long this has
OL,9,Fbeen going on possibly 10 days they
OL,10,Freckon. Now in between it has been
OL,11,Fcleaned probably but the conditions
OL,12,Fstill continue.
OL,14,F"I raised the question of what are we
OL,15,Fgoing to do and basically told we'll
OL,16,Fdeal with him later, get the rest of
OL,17,Fthe prisoners out for their social
OL,18,Ftime and I just came away from there
OL,19,Fthat day thinking that's not just me,
OL,20,FI'm better than that.
