OL,3,CNo one cared for our safety': Former
OL,4,CHMP Parc employees on working in prison
OL,6,F"I didn't sign up for this and yet
OL,7,FI've probably seen a lot more
OL,8,Ftraumatic things there but that was
OL,9,Fthe tipping point for me, I just
OL,10,Fthought it's no longer the job I want
OL,11,Fit to be and after that I submitted my
OL,12,Fresignation in."
OL,14,FLast week the UK Prisons Minister
OL,15,Facknowledged there were some
OL,16,Fchallenges around security and
OL,17,Frecruiting experienced staff at HMP
OL,18,FParc but rejected calls for the
OL,19,FGovernment to take over saying the
OL,20,Fprison is being "well-run".
