OL,3,CNo one cared for our safety': Former
OL,4,CHMP Parc employees on working in prison
OL,6,FITV Wales have spoken to several
OL,7,Fformer workers at Parc - some directly
OL,8,Femployed by G4S, others who regularly
OL,9,Fvisited the prison as agency or
OL,10,Fsupport staff.
OL,12,FThey all questioned the security and
OL,13,Fsearching arrangements there.
OL,15,FOne told us in 10 years of working in
OL,16,FParc, they were never searched.
OL,18,FShe said she thought it would be
OL,19,F"quite easy" to bring contraband into
OL,20,Fthe prison "because of lack of
OL,21,Fsecurity."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
