OL,3,CNo one cared for our safety': Former
OL,4,CHMP Parc employees on working in prison
OL,6,FShe said at times the lack of staff
OL,7,Fmade her fear for her own safety.
OL,9,F"There was never any radios available
OL,10,Ffor us so we could be in any part of
OL,11,Fthe prison without supervision of
OL,12,Fofficers or whatever. You know, I've
OL,13,Fworked in other prisons and not felt
OL,14,Fthe way I've felt in Parc. We got to
OL,15,Fthe stage where we were going in as
OL,16,Ftwos because we didn't have the
OL,17,Freliability of the officer staff to
OL,18,Fhelp us."
