OL,3,CNo one cared for our safety': Former
OL,4,CHMP Parc employees on working in prison
OL,6,FAnother former worker told us "every
OL,7,Fday is just a challenge to get your
OL,8,Fjob done safely.
OL,10,F"Because of staff shortages and we
OL,11,Fhaven't got the right equipment to
OL,12,Fkeep ourselves safe. The turnover of
OL,13,Fstaff is huge.
OL,15,F"Nobody cared about our safety.
OL,17,F"The prisoners run the jail, not the
OL,18,Fstaff. People are at risk going in
OL,19,Fthere whether you're an inmate or
OL,20,Fstaff.
