OL,3,CNo one cared for our safety': Former
OL,4,CHMP Parc employees on working in prison
OL,6,F"I suffered with anxiety and panic
OL,7,Fattacks. I never felt this way going
OL,8,Finto other prisons like Cardiff or
OL,9,FSwansea, it only would happen as I was
OL,10,Fgoing into Parc. I ended up having to
OL,11,Fhave counselling and go on medication."
OL,13,FWe put all of these accounts to G4S
OL,14,Fwho are the private firm operating the
OL,15,Fprison. Responding on safety and
OL,16,Fstaffing, they say it is their
OL,17,Fpriority. They added the staff to
OL,18,Fprisoner ratio is in accordance with
OL,19,FPrison and Probation Service
OL,20,Frequirements, as is the allocation of
OL,21,Fradio equipment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
