OL,3,CNo one cared for our safety': Former
OL,4,CHMP Parc employees on working in prison
OL,6,FA strategy to drive recruitment and
OL,7,Fretention is in place.
OL,9,FG4S strongly refutes claims that staff
OL,10,Fare asked to work 24 hour shifts.
OL,12,FWhen we put the security concerns to
OL,13,Fthe organisation, we were told that
OL,14,Fthe organisation has a zero-tolerance
OL,15,Fapproach towards drugs and uses a
OL,16,Frange of tactics to root them out and
OL,17,Fprevent them coming into the prison.
OL,18,FThat includes random and intelligence-
OL,19,Fled searches of prisoners, visitors
OL,20,Fand staff.
